## Architecture Overview

The backend follows a **layered DDD architecture** adapted for FastAPI:

```
app/
├── domain/           # Business logic, entities, value objects, repository interfaces
├── application/      # Use cases, services — orchestrates domain
├── infrastructure/   # SQLAlchemy repos, Supabase client, external adapters
└── presentation/     # FastAPI routers — thin entry points, delegate to application layer
```

**Dependency rule**: outer layers depend on inner layers. Domain has zero dependencies on infrastructure or FastAPI.

```
presentation → application → domain ← infrastructure
```

